Core Capabilities
- Supports 4K video editing with a timeline for precise adjustments and layering.
- Offers over 300 effects, transitions, and titles to enhance video creativity.
- Utilizes AI-driven features like Instant Cutter and Smart Rendering for efficient processing.
- Provides multi-track timeline editing for complex video projects and audio synchronization.
- Exports videos in various formats, including MP4, AVI, and MOV, at high speeds.

